	<body>
		<div class="rebecca">
			in memory of:<br>
			{`rebecca: { color: #663399 }`}<br>
			💜<a href="https://meyerweb.com/eric/thoughts/2014/06/19/rebeccapurple/" target="_blank">rebeccapurple</a>
		</div>
		<div class="content">
			<div class="content-container">
				<div class="portrait-container">
					<img class="portrait" src="/images/portrait.jpeg" alt="Myself as a painting" />
					<div class="social">
						<ul>
							{socialIcons.map((icon) => (
								<li>
									<a href={icon.url} target="_blank">
										<img src={icon.loc} alt={icon.alt} />
									</a>
								</li>
							))}
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="intro">
					<p>Hey there! 👋</p><br />
					<p>I'm a web and mobile developer based in the USA 🇺🇸, specializing in creating custom websites and web applications that are both functional and beautiful. Whether you're looking to build something from the ground up or improve your current setup, I’m passionate about turning ideas into reality. I also enjoy mentoring and helping others learn along the way!</p><br>
					<p>Outside of coding, I’m usually indulging in sushi 🍣, solving math puzzles, or exploring the outdoors 🌳.</p><br>
					<p>I'm currently open to new projects and collaborations, so feel free to reach out via email or connect with me on social media. Let’s build something amazing together! 😄</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
